trans-unit.source: Contains values used as identifiers for <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IRangeValueProvider" />.
trans-unit.target: Enthält Werte, die als Bezeichner für <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IRangeValueProvider" /> verwendet werden.

trans-unit.source: These values are used by UI Automation providers.
UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent fields in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TransformPattern>.
trans-unit.target: Benutzeroberflächenautomatisierungs-Clientanwendungen verwenden, sollten die entsprechenden Felder im <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TransformPattern>.

trans-unit.source: Identifies the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IRangeValueProvider.IsReadOnly" /> property.

trans-unit.source: The pattern [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_id](~/includes/tlasharptla-id-md.md)] is passed to methods such as <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPattern%2A> to specify the pattern to return.
